	   <tr><td colspan=2>I love this thing, sure no proc. boo-hoo, lol ... My little inkie no strength having butt has always had a hell of a time doing melee damage. Being somewhat poor I have never had the Noct, or Goo covered knights blade, etc option for 1HS - so have settled for the centi LS route and plated shield (free), that is - until I got this thing. Now I hit regularly for 88 + and sometimes as much as 230 (when strength recourse procs like a fool) and this is still fast enough to hold either hold or obtain aggro. Best of all I lost only 10 Ac by switching - not alot of negatives for this in my book.<br><br>-Uteunglachial Argonthiel<br>Knight of the 51st Shadows<br><br>&nbsp;<br>-Always kick a man when he is down. That way he never gets up again.</td></tr>
