	   <tr><td colspan=2>this is all supply side economics my friend.&nbsp;&nbsp;this weapon is a common drop off of many common mobs in PoJ.  the plane it drops in does not require a raid or any special character flags.  so, every day, many, many of these weapons are brought to market.  people who are high enough in lvl to use one at full capacity likely have better weapons.  so in order to sell them at all, people have had to offer better and better prices to make the demand meet the supply.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
